These are Puzzles for 2x3 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-1::.
There are 3 different favourite colors: mauve, grey, red
The people use 3 different means of transport: tram, quad-bike, van
1. the person driving the quad-bike is in the middle##1
2. the person who likes red is the person driving the van##1
3. the person who likes mauve is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |   2    |    3    |
| Color   | mauve | grey | red   |
| Transport      | tram    | quad-bike  | van |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-2::.
3 different games are played: bridge, billiard, mah-jongg
There are 3 different favourite colors: black, azure, turquise
1. the person who likes black is on the left of the person playing mah-jongg##1
2. the person who likes azure is on the far left##1
3. the person who likes azure is the person playing billiard##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |    3     |
| Game      | billiard | bridge     | mah-jongg      |
| Color   | azure | black | turquise |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-3::.
There are 3 different favourite colors: yellow, blood-red, purple
3 different pets are kept: fish, cat, mouse
1. the person who likes blood-red is on the right of the owner of the cat##1
2. the person who likes purple is on the left of the owner of the mouse##1
3. the person who likes yellow is on the left of the owner of the cat##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |   2    |     3     |
| Color   | yellow | purple  | blood-red       |
| Pet       | fish     | cat | mouse |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-4::.
There are 3 different favourite colors: pink, brown, blood-red
3 different pets are kept: fish, ferret, lizard
1. the person who likes brown is on the right of the owner of the lizard##1
2. the person who likes pink is on the right of the owner of the fish##1
3. the owner of the lizard is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |     2      |      3      |
| Color    | blood-red    | brown     | pink |
| Pet   | lizard | fish | ferret     |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-5::.
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: rose, sunflower, poppy
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: ritmeester, montecristo, aristoff
1. the montecristo-smoker is the person who growspoppy##1
2. the montecristo-smoker is on the right of the person who growsrose##1
3. the person who growspoppy is on the right of the ritmeester-smoker##1
4. the person who growsrose is in the middle##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |    2     |    3     |
| Flower         | sunflower | rose     | poppy |
| Cigar   | aristoff        | ritmeester | montecristo    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-6::.
3 different pets are kept: snake, lizard, fish
There are 3 different favourite colors: emerald, purple, ebony
1. the owner of the snake is on the right of the person who likes emerald##1
2. the owner of the lizard is on the right of the person who likes purple##1
3. the owner of the fish is the person who likes emerald##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |     2     |   3   |
| Pet        | fish | snake      | lizard  |
| Color   | emerald       | purple | ebony |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-7::.
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: october, november, september
There 3 different types of food: mango, lemon, tomato
1. the person who's birthday is in september is on the left of the person who's birthday is in october##1
2. the person who's birthday is in november is the person eating lemon##1
3. the person eating mango is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2     |   3    |
| Birthday   | september      | october     | november    |
| Food           | mango | tomato | lemon |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-8::.
There are 3 different nationalities: spanish, indonesian, italian
There are 3 different favourite beverages: sprite, cola, almond-milk
1. the person drinking cola is on the right of the spanish##1
2. the italian is on the left of the person drinking almond-milk##1
3. the indonesian is the person drinking cola##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |     2     |     3      |
| Nationality    | italian | spanish | indonesian      |
| Beverage   | sprite     | almond-milk | cola |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-9::.
The people use 3 different means of transport: airplane, trike, subway
The people have 3 different jobs:  coach, firefighter, teacher
1. the coach is the person driving the trike##1
2. the firefighter is on the far right##1
3. the person driving the trike is on the right of the person driving the subway##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |     2      |   3    |
| Transport   | subway | trike | airplane  |
| Job     | teacher     | coach      | firefighter |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-10::.
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: pall-mall, montecristo, prince
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: rock, hip-hop, r&b
1. the fan of r&b is on the right of the montecristo-smoker##1
2. the fan of r&b is on the far right##1
3. the fan of rock is on the left of the prince-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2     |   3    |
| Cigar      | pall-mall   | montecristo    | prince    |
| Music-Genre   | hip-hop | rock | r&b |

