.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-11::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: traveling, filmmaking, card-games
There 3 different types of food: avocado, pumpkin, eggplant
1. the person who's hobby is card-games is the person eating avocado##1
2. the person eating avocado is on the left of the person who's hobby is filmmaking##1
3. the person eating eggplant is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2     |   3   |
| Hobby   | traveling | card-games   | filmmaking  |
| Food   | eggplant    | avocado | pumpkin |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-12::.
City: hamburg, liverpool, new-york
There are 3 different favourite beverages: milk, 7up, juice
1. the person traveling to hamburg is in the middle##1
2. the person traveling to new-york is on the left of the person drinking milk##1
3. the person drinking 7up is on the left of the person traveling to hamburg##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |    3     |
| City   | new-york    | hamburg     | liverpool   |
| Beverage   | 7up | milk | juice |

