.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-13::.
House: gothic-revival, wooden, modern
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: golf, ice-hockey, biathlon
1. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is on the right of the gothic-revival house##1
2. the modern house is in the middle##1
3. the person who's sport is golf is on the right of the modern house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |       1       |     2      |     3      |
| House   | gothic-revival     | modern   | wooden     |
| Sport    | biathlon | ice-hockey | golf |

