3 different games are played: bridge, scrabble, poker
1. the person playing poker is on the left of the person who growsiris##1
2. the person who growsiris is on the left of the person who growstulip##1
3. the person who growstulip is on the right of the person playing bridge##1

.:: Answer ::.
|       |    1     |       2        |      3      |
| Flower   | rose    | iris | tulip |
| Game   | poker | bridge     | scrabble        |

