House: modern, wooden, victorian
1. the person playing whist is on the far right##1
2. the victorian house is on the left of the person playing whist##1
3. the person playing domino is on the right of the wooden house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1   |   2   |     3     |
| Game      | go  | domino | whist  |
| House   | wooden | victorian   | modern |

