.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-17::.
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: parkour, skateboarding, lacrosse
There are 3 different favourite beverages: mirinda, sprite, milk
1. the person drinking milk is on the far left##1
2. the person who's sport is parkour is on the far right##1
3. the person drinking mirinda is the person who's sport is lacrosse##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |       2       |     3     |
| Sport           | skateboarding | lacrosse | parkour |
| Beverage   | milk  | mirinda      | sprite |

