.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-18::.
There are 3 different favourite colors: aquamarine, ebony, blood-red
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: hip-hop, folk, techno
1. the fan of techno is on the right of the fan of hip-hop##1
2. the person who likes aquamarine is the fan of techno##1
3. the person who likes blood-red is on the right of the person who likes ebony##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1     |    2     |       3       |
| Color    | ebony | blood-red   | aquamarine        |
| Music-Genre   | folk    | hip-hop | techno |

