.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-19::.
3 different pets are kept: rat, horse, goldfish
The people use 3 different means of transport: motorbike, car, train
1. the person driving the motorbike is on the left of the person driving the train##1
2. the owner of the horse is the person driving the train##1
3. the owner of the goldfish is on the right of the owner of the horse##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |   3    |
| Pet         | rat | horse | goldfish |
| Transport   | motorbike | train     | car  |

