.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-20::.
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: sunflower, tulip, daffodil
The people have 3 different hobbies: chess, dancing, hiking
1. the person who's hobby is dancing is in the middle##1
2. the person who's hobby is hiking is on the left of the person who growssunflower##1
3. the person who growstulip is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |      2       |    3    |
| Flower    | daffodil | sunflower       | tulip  |
| Hobby   | hiking  | dancing | chess |

 